column5: Got out on sunday for 2.5 hours Landed 6 of 12 all walleye. Biggest was 2 pounds....  Sorry no pics still more fun than crappie   The ice is still very sketchy... If you're not sure, don't do it.

that's lots of hits for 2.5 hours must be lots of walleye in that lake would love to try my aquav  underwater camera where theres lots of walleye hey I would just like to find some ice to try it out..soon nice to see guys find ice to fish
Hi crusty,  Where in Ottawa is there Ice?  fishinonthebrain
ottawa's east end... back bays only
yes but I would wait another couple days....
way to go...thats amazing to get that many so quick you were right on them big time...    cheers
